# datadog-metrics decorator

A python decorator that handles DataDog Metrics API calls.


## Usage

```python
@DDMetrics.send(my_token)
def get_my_metric(x):
    # 1. get metric data and build the metric payload
    metric = [
        {
            "metric": "something",
            "points": [[time(), 55]],
            "tags": ['test1', 'test2']
        }
    ]
    # 2. return it
    return metric
```


